cc:Work.dc:title: Six Flower Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: For some reason, I thought this would look better in a shade of purple. Thats why I added the shade to this frame of sorts. I'm not sure how it could be used, but it's here for anyone who needs it... and unlike all the phallic symbols that usually pop up, I'm seeing a vaginal symbol in this one. Maybe I'm just going nuts.
